Here's a rundown of some of the best boba places in Berkeley:

**Highly Rated Options:**

*   **Asha Tea House:** Scores 9.2 and is known for its fantastic boba and matcha, especially the Blood Orange Matcha Latte [usequill](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0).
*   **Yi Fang Taiwan Fruit Tea:** Scores 9.1 and is known for unique fruit teas, with the Mango Pomelo Sago being a popular choice [usequill](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0).
*   **TP Tea:** A popular spot among Cal students on Telegraph Ave, known as the "Yifang of milk teas," with the Tie Guan Yin Milk Tea and Taiwan Classic Milk Tea recommended [reddit](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-2).
*   **Feng Cha Teahouse:** Excels in fruit teas, especially kiwi and citrus blends [bubbleteas](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-3).

**Other Notable Shops:**

*   **Happy Lemon:** A Bay Area chain known for its lemon teas and salted cheese foam drinks [wheree](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-4) [usequill](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0).
*   **Nomni Tea:** Offers a variety of options, including fruit teas, slushies, milk teas, and matchas [usequill](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0).
*   **Sweetheart Cafe:** Conveniently located on Bancroft, offering a classic Honey Green Tea with boba [berkeley](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-5).
*   **Plentea:** Known for healthy and tasty tea, with popular drinks including roast oolong milk tea and fruit teas [discoveredinberkeley](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6).
*   **U Cha:** Located near campus, with the Bomberman or Roasted Oolong Milk Tea recommended [dothebay](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-7).

**Newer Establishments:**

*   **Chicha San Chen:** This Taiwanese chain opened a location on Bancroft Way in February 2025 and is known for its high-quality teas [sfchronicle](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-8) [sfchronicle](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-0).
*   **The Alley:** Opened in Berkeley in 2024, with a recent TikTok post confirming its presence as of July 2025 [discoveredinberkeley](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6) [tiktok](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-1).
*   **Purple Kow:** Has opened a new location in Berkeley [tiktok](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-1).
*   **Teaspoon:** Opened in Berkeley near Cal and University Avenue as of November 2024 [bayareatelegraph](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-3).
*   **One Milk Tea Berkeley:** Preparing to open on Martin Luther King Jr Way [whatnow](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-9) [whatnow](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-2).
*   **Zero&:** Set to open later in 2025 in the Telegraph District [discoveredinberkeley](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6).

With so many options, Berkeley offers a diverse range of boba experiences to explore!
